    <item>
      <title>工党大选获胜，英国国内股市今年涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-stocks-lead-europe-rally-on-labour-s-landslide-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，激发了人们对政治稳定可能支撑经济增长反弹的希望，与英国国内经济相关的股票一度出现今年以来的最大涨幅。欧洲股市也普遍上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-stocks-lead-europe-rally-on-labour-s-landslide-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于抛售担忧持续，比特币跌至 2 月以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心政府、交易所破产的债权人以及陷入困境的加密矿工可能抛售比特币，比特币连续第四个交易日下跌，跌至 2 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
